{"tid":1691220,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實要離間D差佬真係話都無咁易，但大家真係唔好咁做","createTime":"2019-11-03T14:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T16:17:20.000Z","uid":19002,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b8c3742a48d47923837e72767662f57217ec7da6","tid":1691220,"uid":19002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:41:30.000Z","msg":"相信大家都有見過依個熱門post<br />\n<br />\n「正能量post」前線警已經不受控制<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1690906\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1690906</a><br />\n<br />\n其實只要每次發生D咩事都凈起個commander底<br />\n咁好快佢地就會叫班散仔唔好搞咁多野<br />\n<br />\n但係<br />\n1. 根本成班都癲晒，勁憎示威者，見人就想打，仲邊會聽指揮<br />\n2. 又唔係起佢底，佢驚條撚咩<br />\n<br />\n最後班白衫就會好憎班前線，想加強對佢地既control<br />\n但班散仔邊會肯，最後會發展成點大家都心裡有數啦<br />\n<br />\n當去到咁上下果陣，突然又起得返打人果個底，你估下班散仔會點諗?<br />\n邊個篤我出黎? 篤我出黎邊個會有好處?<br />\n<br />\n以上都只係我既假設，希望大家唔好咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ac2f4977966b706d7baa208d17a603eb8d3031","tid":1691220,"uid":297569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:42:46.000Z","msg":"［警世］唔好咁易受風向影響<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691168</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"69e2001a0d7a0be1266e71613bf52d1cea46d76b","tid":1691220,"uid":293921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:43:57.000Z","msg":"wa"},{"pid":"5f4f90b880ce46df26d020bb592a998041cd9e46","tid":1691220,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:48:26.000Z","msg":"之前唔知聽邊隻狗講過<br />\n散仔同散仔之間好frd<br />\n但散仔唔妥白衫<br />\n白衫都唔妥散仔架啦<br />\n而家白衫幫自己搵定後路推班散仔去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c364023eebca979054fffa1008ef45a9eb180c35","tid":1691220,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:50:13.000Z","msg":"散仔低層預做condom<br />\n有幾多人會係好老細幫啲細攬 我做咁耐野就冇見過<br />\n斜膊推比人就成日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e20aaa81481c05b732c70819c1ed572b5163124","tid":1691220,"uid":291947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:53:12.000Z","msg":"condom黎姐"},{"pid":"392c0ddd31fe1a11b965e01ea05472deee7f8b7f","tid":1691220,"uid":19002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:58:05.000Z","msg":"推一推，大家唔好咁做"},{"pid":"22ee29074a4938d65582176f45f19a91d8622bd1","tid":1691220,"uid":19002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:13:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"52c1ff94e14eab67d58bb7034c473bbc91b0e191","tid":1691220,"uid":31572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:14:34.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"334e42ce097d368f94e085cd449b698615f43ba2","tid":1691220,"uid":322274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:17:20.000Z","msg":"曱近平<br />\n甴近平<br />\n香港警甴"}]}